{"data": [{"id": "4742579", "title": "Google: Still The Best Tech Mega-Cap Stock Entering 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Google office building in the Company\"s campus in Silicon Valley' data-id=\"1154834209\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5294px\" height=\"3529px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Over the last year, Alphabet's (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOG\" title=\"Alphabet Inc.\">GOOG</a></span>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOGL\" title=\"Alphabet Inc.\">GOOGL</a>) stock has performed in line with the broader market, with the total return matching that of the S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust\">SPY</a>). However, the company's fundamentals have continued to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742579-google-still-the-best-tech-mega-cap-stock-entering-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 14:45:33"}, {"id": "4742577", "title": "DAPP: VanEck's Excellent ETF For Bitcoin, Crypto Exchanges, And Blockchain Exposure", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488104305/image_1488104305.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"The Power of Crypto currency and digital wallets. Transforming Industries and Customer Service. A Look into the Future. Yellow Bitcoin icon on smart phone. 3D render\" data-id=\"1488104305\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"912px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488104305/image_1488104305.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488104305/image_1488104305.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488104305/image_1488104305.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488104305/image_1488104305.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488104305/image_1488104305.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488104305/image_1488104305.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488104305/image_1488104305.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488104305/image_1488104305.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">da-kuk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The VanEck Digital Transformation ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DAPP\" title=\"VanEck Digital Transformation ETF\">DAPP</a></span>) is a diversified yet relatively bold bet on the future of cryptocurrencies and blockchain technology. The DAPP portfolio gives investors strong exposures to Bitcoin, digital asset exchanges, crypto miners, and other blockchain-based infrastructure companies. DAPP is +142% over the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488104305/image_1488104305.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742577-dapp-vaneck-excellent-etf-for-bitcoin-crypto-exchanges-and-blockchain-exposure", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 14:30:00"}, {"id": "4742576", "title": "Gibson Energy: Get Dividend Growth And A 6.5%+ Yield", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/146601285/image_146601285.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil refinery, Hamburg, Germany\" data-id=\"146601285\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/146601285/image_146601285.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/146601285/image_146601285.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/146601285/image_146601285.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/146601285/image_146601285.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/146601285/image_146601285.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/146601285/image_146601285.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/146601285/image_146601285.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/146601285/image_146601285.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Hans-Peter Merten/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Gibson Energy</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">TSX:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GEI:CA\" title=\"Gibson Energy Inc.\">GEI:CA</a></span>) offers investors a compelling combination of a high yield today with the potential to hike the payout going forward. It also trades at a quite reasonable valuation and has seen recent</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/146601285/image_146601285.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742576-gibson-energy-get-dividend-growth-and-a-6-5-percent-plus-yield", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 14:16:55"}, {"id": "4742575", "title": "Dogecoin: Unleash Elon's Beast", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94929156/image_94929156.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dangerous dog with three heads at night\" data-id=\"94929156\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94929156/image_94929156.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94929156/image_94929156.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94929156/image_94929156.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94929156/image_94929156.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94929156/image_94929156.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94929156/image_94929156.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94929156/image_94929156.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94929156/image_94929156.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Grafissimo/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis Summary</h2> <p>Dogecoin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DOGE-USD\" title=\"Dogecoin USD\">DOGE-USD</a>) has appreciated 160% in the last month, and it seems like the rally could keep going over the next few months as Altseason takes hold.</p> <p>The appeal to investing in DOGE continues</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/94929156/image_94929156.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742575-dogecoin-doge-unleash-elon-musk-beast", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 14:07:03"}, {"id": "4742568", "title": "Essex Property Trust: Limited Supply Enables Further Growth", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1746733875/image_1746733875.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pink sunrise lighting over residential area of San Francisco with Oakland Bay Bridge and view of bay\" data-id=\"1746733875\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1746733875/image_1746733875.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1746733875/image_1746733875.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1746733875/image_1746733875.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1746733875/image_1746733875.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1746733875/image_1746733875.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1746733875/image_1746733875.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1746733875/image_1746733875.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1746733875/image_1746733875.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Nicholas Klein/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of Essex Property Trust (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ESS\" title=\"Essex Property Trust, Inc.\">ESS</a></span>) have been a solid performer over the past year, gaining 35%, as the relatively light apartment supply in California has supported results. Its geographic positioning has made Essex a fairly defensive</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1746733875/image_1746733875.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742568-essex-property-trust-limited-supply-enables-further-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 14:00:00"}, {"id": "4742578", "title": "China Is Now The Second-Largest FTSE WGBI Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Multi exposure of virtual abstract financial graph interface on Chinese flag and sunset sky background, financial and trading concept\" data-id=\"1322520591\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4500px\" height=\"3000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Igor Kutyaev</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Ryuichi Urino, Director - FICC Japan Lead</em></p> <p><strong>The FTSE World Government Bond index's phased inclusion of Chinese government bonds is now complete.</strong></p> <p>In March 2021, <a href=\"https://www.lseg.com/content/dam/ftse-russell/en_us/documents/country-classification/fixed-income-country-classification-march-2021-results.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">FTSE Russell announced a phased inclusion of Chinese government bonds (CGBS) in our flagship</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742578-china-second-largest-ftse-wgbi-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 13:35:00"}, {"id": "4742567", "title": "EV Company News For The Month Of November 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354072964/image_1354072964.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Couple using mobile phone while their electric car is charged\" data-id=\"1354072964\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354072964/image_1354072964.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354072964/image_1354072964.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354072964/image_1354072964.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354072964/image_1354072964.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354072964/image_1354072964.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354072964/image_1354072964.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354072964/image_1354072964.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354072964/image_1354072964.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SimonSkafar/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Welcome to the November 2024 edition of Electric Vehicle (EV) company news.</p> <p>The past month saw another great month of sales and another all time record high for EV sales. We also heard more news of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1354072964/image_1354072964.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742567-ev-company-news-november-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 13:28:31"}, {"id": "4742566", "title": "Twin Disc: Best-Case Scenario Looks Like Near-Term Consolidation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172361305/image_172361305.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"luxury motor yacht\" data-id=\"172361305\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1010px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172361305/image_172361305.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172361305/image_172361305.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172361305/image_172361305.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172361305/image_172361305.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172361305/image_172361305.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172361305/image_172361305.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172361305/image_172361305.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172361305/image_172361305.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">laughingmango/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inl